Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Westminster, CO
Description: A beautiful subhurb of Denver where I grew up.

Name: Estest Park, CO
Description: A lovely mountain town just outside of Rocky Mountain National Park. Just a short drive away from the Denver-Metro Area, this is a lovely vacation spot with fun for all ages

Name: Coe College
Description: Coe College, founded in 1851, is a small liberal arts college located in Iowa's second largest city. The school colors are Crimson and Gold and the mascot is the Kohawk. It is my alma mater.

Name: Glacier National Park
Description: Glacier has gorgeous hikes and lots of lakes. It is also located close to the Canadian Border. My favorite part of my childhood visit was horse back riding

Name: Moshi, Tanzania
Description: Moshi is a town in Tanzania located near Mt. Kilimanjaro, the highest mountain in Africa. Moshi has many farms and a bustling urban center with busy markets and nightclubs.
